sentences.english: Fishermen moor their boats at a seasonal camp at the western end of the park.
sentences.chinese: 在公園西端，漁民們把船停泊在一個季節性營地。

sentences.english: The belt is a westward-opening crescent.
sentences.chinese: 成礦帶呈西端張開的新月狀。

sentences.english: Similar troop movements were observed toward the Russian enclave of Abkhazia in the far west of the country.
sentences.chinese: 在阿布哈茲的西端，也有類似的軍隊行動。

sentences.english: The westernmost sharp angle is designed for landscape continuation of the previous three phases.
sentences.chinese: 最西端的尖角型則設計爲前三期主景觀帶的延續。

sentences.english: Transpiration was found to be higher in the west end, where most temperate desert species were distributed.
sentences.chinese: 蒸騰速率在溫帶荒漠植物分佈的西端出現升高的趨勢。

sentences.english: Tangxinzhai gold deposit is located in the northwest part of Laizishan anticline.
sentences.chinese: 塘新寨金礦位於賴子山背斜北西端。

sentences.english: The west end water depth wave is small, natural good harbour.
sentences.chinese: 西端水深浪小，天然良港。
